_sText:
This is my first map creation and I always wanted to make a maze. 

------READ HERE ABOUT THE MAP------
This is a cqb map for minigames or custom maps tdm. This map was intended for camping but since you have a limited supply of ammo it will be harder. You start out with a pistol and will find plenty of guns around the map. You will likely find a gun before dying. This map is good for 10-20 people.
